Text:
It's over 100 degrees around here - who the heck is thinking about Christmas!  But thanks for this anyway.  I think Tom Paxton was brilliant!  (So did Peter Paul and Mary).  

And SEED people!  I only see a few upping about 13%
I guess I was premature with my compliments.  No one seeded this - I finally gave up.  Would have been nice.  Took away my +1.  :-(
